ca.gedge.opgraph.extensions
Interface Publishable

All Known Implementing Classes:
ForEachNode, MacroNode
public interface Publishable

An extension that allows a field of a node to be "published". This extension is intended for nodes with the CompositeNode extension, so that they can expose fields of nodes in their composite graph to be exposed to the graph in which the parent node is located.
